@startuml
title ElectroCorp Web App - Billing Frontend Bounded Context Layers
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

package "Billing Frontend Bounded Context" {
  class "Domain" as Frontend_billing_Domain <<layer>>
  class "Application" as Frontend_billing_Application <<layer>>
  class "Infrastructure" as Frontend_billing_Infrastructure <<layer>>
  class "Presentation" as Frontend_billing_Presentation <<layer>>
}

Frontend_billing_Presentation ..> Frontend_billing_Application : user actions / state
Frontend_billing_Application ..> Frontend_billing_Domain : models and rules
Frontend_billing_Application ..> Frontend_billing_Infrastructure : API services / adapters
Frontend_billing_Infrastructure ..> Frontend_billing_Domain : resources and mappers
Frontend_billing_Presentation ..> Frontend_billing_Domain : view models

note bottom of Frontend_billing_Application
Detailed class diagrams for each layer are available in docs/diagrams/class/frontend/layers/billing.
end note

@enduml
